notes.p: The model reproduces the time evolution of several species as depicted in Fig 4 of the paper. Events have been used to reset cell mass when the value of M-phase promoting factor (MPF) decreases through 0.1. The model was successfully tested on Cell Designer.

This model originates from BioModels Database: A Database of Annotated Published Models. It is copyright (c) 2005-2007 The BioModels Team.
For more information see the terms of use.
The two events are used to reset the cell mass (divide by two) when MPF decreases through 0.1
